<h1>Let's See What We Can See (Everybody Online And Looking Good)</h1>
<h2><span class="vcard"><a class="fn url" href="/schedule/mikemigurski">Mike Migurski</a></span> and <span class="vcard"><a href="/schedule/bencerveny" class="fn url">Ben Cerveny</a></span></h2>

